==Dialogue==
{{Dialogue Start}}
;(First interaction)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 504006001: Config/Level/Mission/5040060/Act/Act504006001.json-->
::'''Demetria:''' These olives today taste pretty good. You should try some... By the way, Hecate's expedition squad set off on another adventure yesterday.
::'''Cassondra:''' Yeah, they've been moving around a lot lately... Oh, these olives are really something. I'll have a few more.
::'''Demetria:''' I heard they're prepping for an in-depth exploration up northeast, but that area's been deserted for ages, right? Wonder if there are any dangers lurking...
::'''Cassondra:''' There are always dangers, but you know how skilled she is, right? Even if she bumps into some wild Titankins, she can probably finagle her way out unscathed.
::'''Demetria:''' True, but... didn't one of the expeditions get struck by the black tide and suffer heavy losses last month? Hmm, maybe you could do a little divination for me?
::'''Cassondra:''' Come on... Fine, I'll cut you a deal this time.
::'''Cassondra:''' See? Told you not to worry. Remember what Talanton teaches us, "Though danger may swoop like an eagle, let your vigilance guide you like a clever fox." Stay alert, and you'll be just fine.
::'''Cassondra:''' Well, I should get going...
::'''Demetria:''' Hey, hold on a sec!
::'''Cassondra:''' What's up? It's just an apple and a pomegranate. You're not going to take them back now, are you? Praise the Scale of Justice, this is my fair payment for the service.
::'''Demetria:''' Ah, got it. In that case, I suppose Talanton wouldn't approve of me slipping you a few extra figs. What a pity. They were picked at the {{Rubi|Entry Hour|dawn}}, and they look so fresh...
::'''Cassondra:''' Oh, wait, wait! I'll never say no to figs! Let me try some for you... Hmm, these do taste great... Oh? Do you have a customer now? I'll leave you to it.
::'''Demetria:''' Welcome... Hey, you must be the outlander brought back by Lord Phainon, right? You seem like quite the charming one.
::'''Demetria:''' Welcome to Okhema, young one. How are you finding life here so far?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} It's okay.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504006018-->
:::'''Cassondra:''' Aha, it can take some time for everyone to get used to things at first, but once you do, you'll see that Okhema is quite cozy &mdash; that goes for the weather, the surroundings, and the lifestyle.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Living here is a real bliss!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504006020-->
:::'''Cassondra:''' Aha! That's great to hear! This holy city, blessed by Kephale, remains unharmed by the black tide. Over time, you'll find that Okhema is quite cozy &mdash; that goes for the weather, the surroundings, and the lifestyle.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Some people here seem a bit unfriendly.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504006022-->
:::'''Cassondra:''' I see... It can take some time for everyone to get used to things at first, but once you do, you'll find that the people here are actually pretty friendly.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504006023-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504006023-->
::'''Cassondra:''' I hope you and your companions settle in quickly, young one. If you need anything, don't hesitate to ask for my help.
;(Subsequent interactions)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 504006002: Config/Level/Mission/5040060/Act/Act504006002.json-->
::'''Demetria:''' Here we meet again, young one. Interested in checking out the fresh fruits picked today?
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
:<!--Open NPC Menu-->
:{{DIcon}} I'd like to check out the fresh fruits here.
::'''Demetria:''' Sure thing. Feel free to sample anything that catches your eye.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Apple, please.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504006213-->
