::{{DIcon|Exit}} I think I'm good for now.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504006235-->
:::'''Demetria:''' Sure! You're always welcome here, young one.
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
:::<!--Ends the current performance-->
:{{DIcon}} Do you need my help with anything?
::'''Demetria:''' Haha, thank you, but there's no need to be a stranger, young one. I enjoy spending time with you young folks. Feel free to drop by anytime for a chat, and that would already make me very happy.
::'''Demetria:''' But then again... I do have a small favor to ask. Half a year ago, my daughter and son-in-law went on an expedition away from the city, and they haven't been heard from since.
::'''Demetria:''' So... if you ever find yourself leaving the city, could you be on the lookout for any information about them? I'd really appreciate it!
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
:{{DIcon|Exit}} I'm busy, so I'll be heading off.
::'''Demetria:''' Sure! You're always welcome here, young one.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
{{Dialogue End}}
